      "rationale": "Code verification performed using method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations and the scalar hemolysis transport equation. Observed order of accuracy: 1.97 for velocity (theoretical: 2.0), 1.94 for pressure, 1.89 for hemolysis scalar. All within 5% of theoretical order, confirming absence of coding errors in discretization schemes. Taylor-Green vortex benchmark also executed with energy spectrum agreement to within 2% at resolved scales.",
