      "rationale": "Systematic mesh refinement study conducted with four mesh levels (0.8M, 3.2M, 12.8M, 51.2M cells, refinement ratio r=2). Richardson extrapolation applied to hemolysis index, pressure head, and peak wall shear stress. Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index on finest mesh: 2.3% (fine-grid GCI). Apparent order of convergence p=1.94, consistent with second-order schemes. Asymptotic range confirmed (GCI_fine/r^p × GCI_coarse < 1.05). Temporal discretization verified with Courant number study; CFL=0.5 selected for all production runs.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
